"{\"uid\": \"thelocal.es-20240728-nadal-may-skip-olympic-singles-after-alcaraz-dream-team-win\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Local Europe ABV\\u00e4stmannagatan 43113 25 StockholmSweden  Rafael Nadal said Saturday that he does not know if he will play singles at the Paris Olympics after picking up a thigh injury in training.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 60, \"end\": 72, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal is due to face Hungary's Marton Fucsovics in the first round on Sunday and victory would hand him a 60th career clash with old rival Novak Djokovic.\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 222, \"end\": 229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999628447398791, \"rank\": 3.7156233345412486e-05, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 232, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\", \"score\": 0.9999999956035026, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marton Fucsovics\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\"}, {\"begin\": 340, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know what's going to happen, I do not know if I am going to play tomorrow or not,\\\" said the 38-year-old Spaniard, who is at his farewell Olympics and is also in the men's doubles.\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 546, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.7062453910913996, \"rank\": 0.41538003082129815, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will talk to my people and make the smartest decision that I can to have the best chance of bringing a medal home, so let us see.\\\"\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 681, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal, who has been plagued by injuries throughout his career, teamed up with Carlos Alcaraz for the first time and defeated Argentina's Maximo Gonzalez and Andres Molteni 7-6 (7/4), 6-4 in front of a packed, raucous crowd under the roof on Court Philippe Chatrier.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 761, \"end\": 775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 0.9999937079403616, \"rank\": 6.2912253153907994e-06, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_Davis_Cup_team\"}, {\"begin\": 820, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1ximo_Gonz\\u00e1lez\", \"score\": 0.9999999983701855, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maximo Gonzalez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1ximo_Gonz\\u00e1lez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1ximo_Gonz\\u00e1lez\"}, {\"begin\": 924, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Court Philippe Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ ALSO:IN DEPTH: Why is Spain so good at sport?\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999985357135, \"rank\": 1.463515332672851e-09, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal, a singles gold medallist at the 2008 Beijing Olympics and doubles title winner at Rio four years later, appeared on court with a bandage strapped around his right thigh.\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1091, \"end\": 1094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999478579372636, \"rank\": 5.214478189422984e-05, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics is just his seventh tournament of 2024, in a season where he has also battled a hip injury and seen his singles ranking plummet to 161.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes more is not always more, sometimes more is less,\\\" added Nadal over the decision he faces.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just enjoying the moment playing doubles together with Carlos,\\\" added Nadal, who featured in the opening ceremony on Friday when he carried the Olympic torch.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1597254973094055e-27, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has been an unforgettable day for me today and an unforgettable day yesterday.\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am enjoying every single moment, having the best experience possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hours earlier when Alcaraz had opened his singles campaign with a straights sets victory over Hady Habib, the 21-year-old said it was a \\\"dream\\\" to play alongside his compatriot Nadal.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1774, \"end\": 1781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.077175951754302e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 1849, \"end\": 1859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hady_Habib\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hady Habib\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hady_Habib\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hady_Habib\"}, {\"begin\": 1932, \"end\": 1937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1597254973094055e-27, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The duo appeared to a standing ovation on the same packed court where Nadal won 14 French Opens and Alcaraz collected his first just last month.\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 2084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2023, \"end\": 2029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7144591838131668, \"rank\": 0.2328428456240631, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2040, \"end\": 2047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.077175951754302e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gonzalez and Molteni, the sixth seeds, entered the arena to a chorus of boos in the aftermath of a recent racism row between Argentina and France.\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2099, \"end\": 2106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molteni\", \"score\": 0.9999746628167798, \"rank\": 2.5337825347020442e-05, \"text\": \"Molteni\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molteni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molteni\"}, {\"begin\": 2211, \"end\": 2220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 0.9999937079403616, \"rank\": 6.2912253153907994e-06, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_Davis_Cup_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9984644785182606, \"rank\": 0.0015373688601691548, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spanish pair endured a nightmare start when Alcaraz was broken in the first game.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2238, \"end\": 2245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.966743097338883, \"rank\": 0.026024531732087703, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2282, \"end\": 2289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.077175951754302e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having not played doubles on tour since 2022, the rustiness was not surprising.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The greater experience of Nadal was key and the break was quickly retrieved with the veteran's reflexes as razor sharp as ever at the net.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2427, \"end\": 2432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1597254973094055e-27, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alcaraz and Nadal went to three set points in the tiebreaker and a pinpoint backhand down the line by Nadal secured the opener.\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2541, \"end\": 2548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.077175951754302e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 2553, \"end\": 2558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1597254973094055e-27, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 2643, \"end\": 2648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1597254973094055e-27, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gonzalez and Molteni raced to a 3-0 lead in the second set but back came the Spanish pair to level.\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2683, \"end\": 2690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molteni\", \"score\": 0.9999746628167798, \"rank\": 2.5337825347020442e-05, \"text\": \"Molteni\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molteni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molteni\"}, {\"begin\": 2747, \"end\": 2754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.966743097338883, \"rank\": 0.026024531732087703, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal secured another key break with a rasping backhand return to allow him and his partner to lead 5-4 and the opportunity to serve for the match.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That honour fell to the 22-time Grand Slam title champion and victory was secured when Alcaraz slapped the winning forehand crouching at the net.\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 3065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3007, \"end\": 3014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.077175951754302e-19, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please sign up or log in to continue reading  Join the conversation in our comments section below.Share your own views and experience and if you have a question or suggestion for our journalists then email us atnews@thelocal.es.Please keep comments civil, constructive and on topic - and make sure to read ourterms of usebefore getting involved.\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please log inhereto leave a comment.\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Local Europe ABV\\u00e4stmannagatan 43113 25 StockholmSweden  By signing up you agree to ourTerms of UseandPrivacy Policy.We will use your email address to send you newsletters as well as information and offers related to your account.\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2025 The Local, All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 3687, \"to\": 3723, \"entities\": []}]}"